name: ledlightsources
overview:
Our Technology

We design and manufacture all our own electronic circuitry. We pride ourselves on producing high quality products. Our emphasis is ensuring that our products are extremely reliable.

We use only LEDs manufactured in Japan or USA. Many other Asian imports are available but their quality and reliability are questionable and do not meet our standards.

The Team

Col Pindar, Inventor and CEO of LEDLight Sources Australia, has worked in electronics and lighting for 35 years. Over the last 10 years he has concentrated on LED Lighting and heads a team of LED Light Experts who nickname him the LEDLight Guru. He has a reputation for fixing difficult-to-solve lighting problems, using only the highest quality LEDs and fittings.

We have provided LED lighting and circuitry in both domestic and commercial properties for under steps, above gardens, under outdoor benches, under-water lights, and internal lighting with unique specifications from lighting designers.
